sequenceDiagram
  participant Client as User device
  participant WG as WireGuard tunnel
  participant VPS as Linux VPS
  participant NAT as VPS NAT
  participant Site as Public internet

  Client->>WG: Send packet to 0.0.0.0/0 route
  WG->>VPS: Encrypted UDP 51820
  VPS->>NAT: Decrypt and forward
  NAT->>Site: Egress from VPS public IP
  Site-->>NAT: Response to VPS public IP
  NAT-->>VPS: Reverse NAT
  VPS-->>WG: Encrypt response
  WG-->>Client: Deliver packet to client

